data.title: Karan Singh Grover
data.meta_description: Karan Singh Grover is an Indian model and actor known for his work in television series such as Dill Mill Gayye and Qubool Hai. He has also starred in Hindi films like Alone and Hate Story 3.
data.text:
Not to be confused with Karan Grover.

Karan Singh Grover (born 23 February 1982)[1][2] is an Indian model and actor known for his work in television series such as Dill Mill Gayye and Qubool Hai. He has also starred in Hindi films like Alone and Hate Story 3.
